ZH: 我这个月要出差到上海。
EN: I have to go on a business trip to Shanghai this month.

ZH: 昨天老板通知我要出差到北京。
EN: Yesterday the boss informed me that I have to go on a business trip to Beijing.

ZH: 我出差的时候会尽量保持联系。
EN: I will try to stay in touch while I'm on the business trip.

ZH: 周末出差的计划被取消了。
EN: The weekend business trip plan got canceled.

ZH: 我已经准备好出差所需要的文件。
EN: I have already prepared all the necessary documents for the business trip.

ZH: 出差期间我会每天给你发短信。
EN: I will text you every day during the business trip.

ZH: 我出差到上海两天。
EN: I will be on a two-day business trip to Shanghai.

ZH: 出差期间请帮我照顾好家里的植物。
EN: Please take care of the plants at home while I am on the business trip.

ZH: 下周公司部分员工要出差到香港。
EN: Some employees from the company will go on a business trip to Hong Kong next week.

ZH: 出差会耽误你的计划吗？
EN: Will the business trip interfere with your plans?

ZH: 出差期间要注意休息不要太过劳累。
EN: Make sure to get enough rest and not overwork yourself during the business trip.

ZH: 我需要办理出差报销手续。
EN: I need to go through the business trip reimbursement procedure.

ZH: 明天早上准备好行李，我们要出差了。
EN: Pack your bags tomorrow morning, we are going on a business trip.

ZH: 出差期间工作日程很紧张。
EN: The work schedule during the business trip is very tight.

ZH: 出差过后要提前登记报销。
EN: Register for reimbursement in advance after the business trip.

ZH: 他每个月都要出差到不同的城市。
EN: He goes on business trips to different cities every month.

ZH: 出差要随身带上需要的文件和资料。
EN: Remember to bring the necessary documents and materials with you on the business trip.

ZH: 出差期间要遵守公司规定。
EN: Follow the company regulations during the business trip.

ZH: 明天出差的同事请记得早点到公司集合。
EN: Colleagues who are going on a business trip tomorrow, please arrive at the company early.

ZH: 出差需要提前订好酒店。
EN: Make sure to book a hotel in advance for the business trip.
